Source: just
Section: misc
Maintainer: Local Builder <builder@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl
Homepage: https://github.com/casey/just

Package: just
Architecture: amd64
Description: Just a command runner.
 just is a handy way to save and run project-specific commands. Commands,
 called recipes, are stored in a file called justfile with a syntax
 inspired by make.
